50|$|<b>Balises</b> are {{differentiated}} {{as being}} either a 'Fixed Data Balise' transmitting {{the same data}} to every train, or a 'Transparent Data Balise' which transmits variable data, also called a 'Switchable' or 'Controllable Balise'. (Note that the word 'fixed' refers to the information transmitted by the balise, not to its physical location. All <b>balises</b> are immobile).|$|E
